o.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab743bff1e0d7818e96205fc16ab4f08cca6aab","tid":84770,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問下啲踩去 非洲，英國嘅痴線佬攞下意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲啲會問下 其實岩岩踩上廣州之前都有問過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfb0414db8cc2a4a13ffa34244710da8bae49ce","tid":84770,"uid":4031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:23:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3836db0b3e8bf98623b951670d3c930d8c90ef5a","tid":84770,"uid":24883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟點做到</blockquote><br />\n用對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0746ac0d453be097ad084c7c104390fcf110ab38","tid":84770,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:42:22.000Z","msg":"加油巴打<br />\n宜家廿到中放唔低份工做呢d咁熱血嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1003805c487113826b319783a35038388b4171d","tid":84770,"uid":11227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"好想去，但體能未必得。。"},{"pid":"783c6973370a0d49fbfe0acf26daeaa1c2b2683b","tid":84770,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油巴打<br />\n宜家廿到中放唔低份工做呢d咁熱血嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身我都有fd鍾意一齊癲 但佢地都係因為份工所以唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者巴打遲啲有機會呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ade4b2e62436e43ea00099613c3bfc06f7b7c22","tid":84770,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想去，但體能未必得。。</blockquote><br />\n其實長途旅行已經係每日鍛煉緊體能<br />\n當然又唔好完全無準備 但唔需要好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c16909c7183dde8f4dd4a3f8607b5c5d901304","tid":84770,"uid":73371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油巴打<br />\n宜家廿到中放唔低份工做呢d咁熱血嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n永遠都唔會太遲<br />\n如果keep住諗而家已經要穩定工作，放唔低份工，到左30歲你就會發現除左港奴之外咩都無做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想做就做，返到黎又係一條好漢返工搵錢，第日回頭望一定唔會後悔，條數點計都值"},{"pid":"3c7ce97f3704d1d6f5213bac0cb14354d5812e1d","tid":84770,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:40:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}